        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"814172\">@Jasin Jiang</span> the trick is to distribute coeff linearly even though it's zero elsewhere, i.e. <code>coeff x^2 (1+x+x^2+x^4) = coeff x^2 1 + coeff x^2 x + coeff x^2 x^2 + coeff x^2 x^4 = 0 + 0 + 1 + 0 = 1</code></p>",
